title: Scott Morrison Biography - Facts, Childhood, Family Life, Achievements
snippet: Scott John Morrison was born on 13 May 1968 in Waverley, Sydney, New South Wales. His father, John Morrison, initially a police commissioner, later became an independent politician, who served on the Waverley Municipal Council for sixteen years.
